  	<h6 class="docs-header">What is escrit?</h6>
  	<p>escrit is a language learning tool that supports you in reading texts in a foreign language. After setting up your account, you can import any text you would like to read, be it from a text book, newspaper or from a book.</p>
    <p>Having imported it, escrit allows you to look up words you do not understand in online dictionaries, and keep track of which words you know and how well you know them. You rate words and they will appear color highlighted in your text as well as in all future texts, reminding you of them.</p>
    <p>Through this kind of quick, productive and extensive reading, you will quickly find your vocabulary naturally expand itself without the frustration of utilizing any complicated software or tools such as flashcards which can easily become boring and frustrating to have to use. Instead, jump right in, take an interesting text in your target language and have some fun learning something new.</p>

