  	<h6 class="docs-header">What languages are supported?</h6>
  	<p>Languages in which words can be clearly separated into words, based on their usage of space or special characters, can theoretically be used in escrit. As such, languages like Japanese or Mandarin, which do not use space characters, can currently not be supported.</p>
    <p>Languages that use space characters, however, work in general. Currently escrit officially supports the following languages:</p>
    <p><em><%= @languages.map {|l| l.name }.to_sentence %></em></p>
